flowchart TD
  A[InspectionRun FINALIZED] --> B[InspectionDefects created]
  B --> C[Generate WorkOrderLineProposals]
  C --> D[Bulk promote -> WorkOrder]
  D --> E[Issue parts from InventoryLocation]
  E --> F[WorkOrder COMPLETE]
  F --> G[Defects RESOLVED]
  F --> H[AssetCostEvent emitted]
  G --> I{Defect severity UNSAFE?}
  I -- Yes --> J[verification_status REQUIRED]
  J --> K[Recheck InspectionRun]
  K --> L{PASSED?}
  L -- Yes --> M[Compliance COMPLIANT]
  L -- No --> N[Compliance OUT_OF_SERVICE]
  F --> O[Create Invoice DRAFT]
  O --> P[Issue Invoice]
  P --> Q[Record Payment]
  P --> R[Outbox -> QBO Push]
